	* acinclude.m4 (AC_SHORT_D_NAME_LEN): Fix compiler warnings in
	the test code.
	* configure.in: Fix compiler warnings in the arguments to
	AC_TRY_WARNINGS. Fix value of NEED_CRYPT_PROTOTYPE - add spaces
	around `=' in the `test' command.

